cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL 

This paper proposes an approach for mapping natural language instructions and raw observations to continuous control of a quadcopter drone, which involves robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The model predicts interpretable position-visitation distributions indicating where the agent should go during execution, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.RO, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.CL.
